You can install <%= vars.ops_manager_first %> on AWS using Terraform.
After you install <%= vars.ops_manager %> on AWS using Terraform, you can install either
the <%= vars.app_runtime_first %> or <%= vars.k8s_runtime_first %> runtime on <%= vars.ops_manager %>.

