## <a id='terraform-pas'></a> Installation procedure

To install <%= vars.ops_manager %> using Terraform:

1. Deploy <%= vars.ops_manager %>. For more information, see [Deploying <%= vars.ops_manager %> on AWS using Terraform](../aws/prepare-env-terraform.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. For more information, see [Configuring BOSH Director on AWS using Terraform](../aws/config-terraform.html).

## <a id='next'></a> Next steps

After you complete the prededing procedures, configure a runtime.

